Create a .gitignore file for a Python reinforcement learning project with the following entries:

## Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

## Virtual environment
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

## Training outputs
checkpoints/
graphs/
rewards.csv
fresh_start.flag

## PyTorch
*.pth
*.pt

## Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

## IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.user

## OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

## Logs
*.log
logs/
